<div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto bg-white p-3 md:p-6"
     data-controller="exercise-checker text-toggle font-controls"
     data-text-toggle-target="content"
     data-font-controls-target="content">

  <%= render 'shared/page_header', pagina: @pagina %>

  <div class="space-y-6">
    <!-- Introduzione -->
    <div>
      <p class="text-gray-700">
        Sai già che i <strong>poligoni regolari</strong> hanno <strong>tutti gli angoli e tutti i lati congruenti</strong>.
        Essi hanno anche altre caratteristiche particolari. Per esempio, i poligoni regolari hanno tanti <strong>assi di simmetria</strong> quanti sono i lati e gli angoli.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Osserva conta e completa -->
    <div>
      <p class="text-gray-700 font-bold mb-4">
        <span class="text-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500">•</span> Osserva, conta e completa.
      </p>

      <!-- Prima riga: 3 poligoni -->
      <div class="grid grid-cols-3 gap-4 mb-6 text-center">
        <div>
          <div class="h-24 flex items-center justify-center mb-2">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 100 100" class="w-20 h-20">
              <polygon points="50,15 85,85 15,85" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" class="text-gray-600"/>
              <line x1="50" y1="15" x2="50" y2="85" stroke="red" stroke-width="1" stroke-dasharray="3,3"/>
              <line x1="15" y1="85" x2="67" y2="50" stroke="red" stroke-width="1" stroke-dasharray="3,3"/>
              <line x1="85" y1="85" x2="33" y2="50" stroke="red" stroke-width="1" stroke-dasharray="3,3"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <p class="text-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-600 font-bold">triangolo equilatero</p>
          <div class="text-gray-700 space-y-1">
            <p>n. lati: <input type="text" data-correct-answer="3" class="w-12 border-b-2 border-dotted border-gray-400 text-center font-bold bg-transparent"></p>
            <p>n. angoli: <input type="text" data-correct-answer="3" class="w-12 border-b-2 border-dotted border-gray-400 text-center font-bold bg-transparent"></p>
            <p>n. assi di simmetria: <input type="text" data-correct-answer="3" class="w-12 border-b-2 border-dotted border-gray-400 text-center font-bold bg-transparent"></p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div>
          <div class="h-24 flex items-center justify-center mb-2">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 100 100" class="w-20 h-20">
              <rect x="20" y="20" width="60" height="60" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" class="text-gray-600"/>
              <line x1="50" y1="20" x2="50" y2="80" stroke="red" stroke-width="1" stroke-dasharray="3,3"/>
              <line x1="20" y1="50" x2="80" y2="50" stroke="red" stroke-width="1" stroke-dasharray="3,3"/>
              <line x1="20" y1="20" x2="80" y2="80" stroke="red" stroke-width="1" stroke-dasharray="3,3"/>
              <line x1="80" y1="20" x2="20" y2="80" stroke="red" stroke-width="1" stroke-dasharray="3,3"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <p class="text-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-600 font-bold">quadrato</p>
          <div class="text-gray-700 space-y-1">
            <p>n. lati: <input type="text" data-correct-answer="4" class="w-12 border-b-2 border-dotted border-gray-400 text-center font-bold bg-transparent"></p>
            <p>n. angoli: <input type="text" data-correct-answer="4" class="w-12 border-b-2 border-dotted border-gray-400 text-center font-bold bg-transparent"></p>
            <p>n. assi di simmetria: <input type="text" data-correct-answer="4" class="w-12 border-b-2 border-dotted border-gray-400 text-center font-bold bg-transparent"></p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div>
          <div class="h-24 flex items-center justify-center mb-2">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 100 100" class="w-20 h-20">
              <polygon points="50,10 95,40 80,90 20,90 5,40" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" class="text-gray-600"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <p class="text-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-600 font-bold">pentagono regolare</p>
          <div class="text-gray-700 space-y-1">
            <p>n. lati: <input type="text" data-correct-answer="5" class="w-12 border-b-2 border-dotted border-gray-400 text-center font-bold bg-transparent"></p>
            <p>n. angoli: <input type="text" data-correct-answer="5" class="w-12 border-b-2 border-dotted border-gray-400 text-center font-bold bg-transparent"></p>
            <p>n. assi di simmetria: <input type="text" data-correct-answer="5" class="w-12 border-b-2 border-dotted border-gray-400 text-center font-bold bg-transparent"></p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Seconda riga: 3 poligoni -->
      <div class="grid grid-cols-3 gap-4 mb-6 text-center">
        <div>
          <div class="h-24 flex items-center justify-center mb-2">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 100 100" class="w-20 h-20">
              <polygon points="50,10 93,30 93,70 50,90 7,70 7,30" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" class="text-gray-600"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <p class="text-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-600 font-bold">esagono regolare</p>
          <div class="text-gray-700 space-y-1">
            <p>n. lati: <input type="text" data-correct-answer="6" class="w-12 border-b-2 border-dotted border-gray-400 text-center font-bold bg-transparent"></p>
            <p>n. angoli: <input type="text" data-correct-answer="6" class="w-12 border-b-2 border-dotted border-gray-400 text-center font-bold bg-transparent"></p>
            <p>n. assi di simmetria: <input type="text" data-correct-answer="6" class="w-12 border-b-2 border-dotted border-gray-400 text-center font-bold bg-transparent"></p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div>
          <div class="h-24 flex items-center justify-center mb-2">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 100 100" class="w-20 h-20">
              <polygon points="50,5 79,21 95,50 79,79 50,95 21,79 5,50 21,21" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" class="text-gray-600"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <p class="text-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-600 font-bold">ottagono regolare</p>
          <div class="text-gray-700 space-y-1">
            <p>n. lati: <input type="text" data-correct-answer="8" class="w-12 border-b-2 border-dotted border-gray-400 text-center font-bold bg-transparent"></p>
            <p>n. angoli: <input type="text" data-correct-answer="8" class="w-12 border-b-2 border-dotted border-gray-400 text-center font-bold bg-transparent"></p>
            <p>n. assi di simmetria: <input type="text" data-correct-answer="8" class="w-12 border-b-2 border-dotted border-gray-400 text-center font-bold bg-transparent"></p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div>
          <div class="h-24 flex items-center justify-center mb-2">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 100 100" class="w-20 h-20">
              <polygon points="50,5 69,12 85,27 93,47 89,68 76,85 56,94 35,91 17,78 8,58 10,37 22,19 40,9" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" class="text-gray-600"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <p class="text-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-600 font-bold">decagono regolare</p>
          <div class="text-gray-700 space-y-1">
            <p>n. lati: <input type="text" data-correct-answer="10" class="w-12 border-b-2 border-dotted border-gray-400 text-center font-bold bg-transparent"></p>
            <p>n. angoli: <input type="text" data-correct-answer="10" class="w-12 border-b-2 border-dotted border-gray-400 text-center font-bold bg-transparent"></p>
            <p>n. assi di simmetria: <input type="text" data-correct-answer="10" class="w-12 border-b-2 border-dotted border-gray-400 text-center font-bold bg-transparent"></p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Poligoni inscritti -->
    <div>
      <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
        Inoltre, se punti un compasso nel centro O del poligono con apertura corrispondente al segmento che congiunge O a uno qualsiasi dei vertici, riesci a circoscrivere al poligono una <strong>circonferenza</strong>, ovvero tutti i vertici del poligono sono punti di una stessa circonferenza.
      </p>
      <div class="flex justify-center">
        <%= image_tag "nvi5_mat/p117/p117_01.jpg", class: "max-w-full md:max-w-2xl", alt: "Poligoni inscritti" %>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Rifletti e completa -->
    <div>
      <p class="text-gray-700 font-bold mb-4">
        <span class="text-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500">•</span> Rifletti e completa.
      </p>
      <ul class="space-y-3 text-gray-700">
        <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
          <span>–</span>
          <span>È possibile dividere i poligoni regolari in tanti triangoli uguali quanti sono i loro lati?
            <label class="inline-flex items-center gap-1 ml-2">
              <input type="checkbox" class="w-4 h-4" data-correct-answer="true">
              <span>Sì</span>
            </label>
            <label class="inline-flex items-center gap-1 ml-2">
              <input type="checkbox" class="w-4 h-4">
              <span>No</span>
            </label>
          </span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
          <span>–</span>
          <span>Ogni triangolo in cui è diviso il poligono ha come base il lato del poligono e come lati i <input type="text" data-correct-answer="raggi" class="w-20 border-b-2 border-dotted border-gray-400 text-center font-bold bg-transparent"> del cerchio.</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
          <span>–</span>
          <span>I triangoli che compongono i poligoni sono triangoli <input type="text" data-correct-answer="isosceli" class="w-24 border-b-2 border-dotted border-gray-400 text-center font-bold bg-transparent"></span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
          <span>–</span>
          <span>Il centro del cerchio è anche il centro del <input type="text" data-correct-answer="poligono" class="w-24 border-b-2 border-dotted border-gray-400 text-center font-bold bg-transparent"></span>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <%= render 'shared/exercise_controls' %>
  </div>
</div>
